    "Helpful empty state copy and straightforward task-entry flow",
    "Consistent visual styling across inputs, list items, and actions"
  ],
  "top_issues": [
    "Error state presentation appears blank and not informative",
    "Low contrast on the Add button and timestamp text",
    "Checkbox, dismiss, and delete controls have small hit areas"
